description:
Carl Filtsch (1830~1845)

Piano Concertino in B minor / Konzertstück in B minor (1842)

The Konzertstück in B minor, written at twelve years of age, 
is Filtsch's magnum opus.


Piano : Hubert Rutkowski
Polish Radio Symphony Orchestra / Łukasz Borowicz
